ello game, http://www.tothello.com/html/reversed_othello_games.html.[15]    Y. Wang, , S. Gelly, "Modifications of UCT and sequence-like simulations for Monte-Carlo go, "CIG 2007, Honolulu, USA, pp. 175–182, 2007.
